Weapon Perks<br />
<br />
Excavation<br />
Hold to fire grenades. Release to detonate all live grenades simultaneously. Grenades stick to surfaces and set targets on fire.<br />
<br />
Volatile Launch<br />
This weapon is optimized for an especially explosive payload. • Greatly increases blast radius • Slightly decreases handling speed • Slightly decreases projectile speed<br />
<br />
Augmented Drum<br />
Heavy, high capacity drum. • Greatly increases magazine size • Greatly decreases reload speed<br />
<br />
Full Auto Trigger System<br />
Holding down the trigger will fire this weapon at full auto.<br />
<br />
Hand-Laid Stock<br />
This weapon is optimized for recoil control. • Increases stability<br />
Weapon Mods<br />
<br />
Default Ornament<br />
Restores your weapon to its default appearance.<br />
<br />
Comstock Lode<br />
Equip this Weapon Ornament to change the appearance of The Prospector.<br />
<br />
Belvedere<br />
Equip this weapon ornament to change the appearance of the Prospector. Once you get an ornament, it's unlocked for all characters on your account.<br />
<br />
Prospector Catalyst<br />
Upgrades this weapon to a Masterwork. It will generate Orbs on multikills and gain a tracker that displays the number of enemies defeated by using it. You can upgrade it to improve its stats and perks.<br />
<br />
Upgrade Masterwork<br />
Defeat enemies and complete the Nightfall strike "The Arms Dealer" during Armsweek with the Prospector equipped to unlock this upgrade.<br />
